name: Lioness close up
description:
(This is a close-up of image, please see Lioness image for actual print)

Limited Edition run of 20, 2 coloured hand pulled screen prints of the original Lioness artwork for La La and the Boo Ya`s debut single released through Congo Natty. Available only through the artist.

 - Printed on off-white High Quality paper
 - Size A-3
 - Numbered and signed by the artist

Prints will be packaged in poster tubes and delivered within 4-6 days of receiving payment, total price includes postage and packaging.  There`s space on the prints for extra signatures, so why not pop them into the tube and take along to the next La La and Boo Ya gig for Marf and Eddie to sign, and have yourself a one-off timeless piece of artwork to treasure for life.  These are the only original signed and numbered run of prints for the official artwork, and there`s only 15 left so get ya paws on one and frame it on your wall with pride.  Here`s the original song...official video coming soon :)

 http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QR8ryIyhgfE

And here`s the superb Congo Natty re-mix...enjoy

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-S2cyWCnRrU

For any other information please feel free to contact
